for helping me out.

17:09.598 --> 17:11.577
Hey, I'm great in a crisis.

17:13.103 --> 17:17.083
Well, I definitely picked
the right person to sit next to.

17:17.107 --> 17:19.785
Actually, is this seat taken?

17:19.809 --> 17:22.048
No.

17:22.071 --> 17:25.090
Okay, you can share my popcorn.

17:25.115 --> 17:27.423
Um, Susan...

17:27.446 --> 17:29.125
This is Becky.

17:29.149 --> 17:31.149
I'll probably be sharing
herpopcorn.

17:34.284 --> 17:36.211
I'll just wait
till the lights go out,

17:36.235 --> 17:37.726
and then I'll...

17:44.063 --> 17:47.050
While I get this going,
can you bring out the buns?

17:47.074 --> 17:48.114
Uh, yeah.

17:52.342 --> 17:55.072
What the hell? You all right?

18:00.079 --> 18:02.228
This isn't lighter fluid.
It's gasoline.

18:02.252 --> 18:03.489
What?

18:03.513 --> 18:06.092
How'd that get in there?

18:06.116 --> 18:07.786
How do you think?

18:12.292 --> 18:14.292
Something smells good
over there.

18:16.626 --> 18:20.176
Well, I don't understand.
Is she trying to kill you?

18:20.200 --> 18:22.848
No, she's trying to piss me off.

18:22.872 --> 18:24.480
Why?

18:24.504 --> 18:26.452
I'm not sure yet,

18:26.476 --> 18:29.084
but I do know
I'm not gonna play along.

18:29.108 --> 18:31.617
We got plenty of burgers
if you want to pop over.

18:31.641 --> 18:34.211
And bring your appetite.

18:47.497 --> 18:49.157
Gaby, the baby.

18:51.901 --> 18:54.380
No, I got up twice already.
It's your turn.

18:54.404 --> 18:56.221
Gaby, I have several
job interviews tomorrow.

18:56.245 --> 18:58.644
I need my sleep.

18:58.668 --> 19:01.238
What aboutmysleep?

19:04.714 --> 19:07.553
You sleep when the baby sleeps.

19:07.577 --> 19:09.255
Every 40 minutes?

19:09.279 --> 19:11.297
When am I supposed
to have a life?

19:11.321 --> 19:13.199
What are you whining about?

19:13.223 --> 19:15.706
You know, xiao-Mei does
all the housework around here.

19:15.730 --> 19:18.334
All you have to do
is take care of the baby.

19:18.358 --> 19:19.835
Fine, fine, fine!

19:23.893 --> 19:25.171
Psst!

19:25.195 --> 19:26.472
Xiao-Mei.

19:26.496 --> 19:28.143
Psst, wake up.

19:28.167 --> 19:30.576
Mrs. Solis?

19:30.600 --> 19:32.178
Something wrong?

19:32.202 --> 19:34.720
The baby won't stop crying,

19:34.744 --> 19:36.727
and I haven't slept
for two days.

19:36.751 --> 19:38.584
Will you please take
Lily for a while? Uh...

19:38.608 --> 19:42.188
Oh, come on. I won't make you
do windows tomorrow.

19:42.212 --> 19:45.160
Okay. What do I do?

19:45.184 --> 19:47.533
Well, she's a baby.
You hold her.

19:47.557 --> 19:49.235
You bounce her

19:49.259 --> 19:52.238
and, I don't know,
maybe sing a little something.

19:52.262 --> 19:54.500
Ahh.

19:54.524 --> 19:56.242
Oh, and xiao-Mei,

19:56.266 --> 19:59.305
Mr. Solis does not need to know about this,
okay? Okay.

19:59.329 --> 20:01.207
Okay.

20:06.336 --> 20:08.784
Yeah, honey, can you
take that downstairs?

20:08.808 --> 20:10.378
Thank you.

20:18.217 --> 20:20.195
Eleanor,
I thought you'd gone to bed.

20:20.219 --> 20:22.698
Oh, no, not yet.
I had to do my hair now.

20:22.722 --> 20:25.309
There's never enough time
in the morning.

20:25.333 --> 20:26.772
Uh, sit.

20:26.796 --> 20:30.276
There's something
I have to discuss with you.

20:30.300 --> 20:32.778
Your father and I
have decided to take Andrew

20:32.802 --> 20:34.310
back to Rhode Island with us.

20:34.334 --> 20:36.211
Really?

20:36.235 --> 20:38.314
And whose idea was that?

20:38.338 --> 20:40.246
Andrew's.

20:40.270 --> 20:44.290
But Henry and I feel
it's the right thing to do.

20:44.314 --> 20:46.924
Absolutely not.

20:49.949 --> 20:51.927
If we leave him here,

20:51.951 --> 20:54.430
the two of you
will wind up in court,

20:54.454 --> 20:56.441
and I'm not going to allow that.

20:56.465 --> 20:57.933
Do you really think

20:57.957 --> 21:01.407
that I am enjoying airing
my dirty laundry in public?

21:01.431 --> 21:04.740
This whole situation
is mortifying.

21:04.764 --> 21:07.418
But I can't back down
because he is my son,

21:07.442 --> 21:09.715
and I need more time
to get through to him.

21:09.739 --> 21:13.248
You never give up.

21:13.272 --> 21:16.452
I've always admired that
about you.

21:16.476 --> 21:17.953
When you were a kid,

21:17.977 --> 21:20.286
you used to make
these peanut butter cookies

21:20.310 --> 21:22.388
that were god-awful.

21:22.412 --> 21:23.859
But you kept baking them,

21:23.883 --> 21:27.363
and you kept forcing everyone
to eat them.

21:28.458 --> 21:31.697
You were so determined
to get them right.

21:31.721 --> 21:34.740
My mother didn't think
they were awful.

21:34.764 --> 21:38.281
When I made those same cookies
for her, she loved them.

21:38.305 --> 21:41.006
Well, some people
praise children

21:41.030 --> 21:43.309
even when they don't deserve it.

21:43.333 --> 21:44.680
Oh, but not you.

21:44.704 --> 21:48.388
With you, I had to work for
every kind word I ever got.

21:48.412 --> 21:51.457
Well, you always resented me
because of my high standards.

21:51.481 --> 21:53.018
No.

21:53.042 --> 21:54.520
I resented you

21:54.544 --> 21:57.024
because those were kick-ass
peanut butter cookies.

21:59.719 --> 22:01.697
We're taking Andrew.

22:01.721 --> 22:04.400
Eleanor, please...

22:04.424 --> 22:06.532
He hates you, Bree.

22:06.556 --> 22:09.635
Your own son.

22:09.659 --> 22:11.937
You know, part of being an adult

22:11.961 --> 22:14.580
is admitting that you've failed,

22:14.604 --> 22:16.882
and then moving on...

22:16.906 --> 22:18.406
With grace.

22:20.109 --> 22:25.320
Do you really think that I am
a failure as a parent?

22:25.344 --> 22:29.031
Well, I'd love to lie
and say something supportive,

22:29.055 --> 22:31.026
but as you pointed out,

22:31.050 --> 22:34.550
that was more
your mother's thing.

22:44.363 --> 22:46.341
Xiao-Mei?

22:46.365 --> 22:48.343
So sorry. I just take break.

22:48.367 --> 22:50.345
Oh, no, xiao-Mei,
that's okay. That's okay.

22:50.369 --> 22:52.848
I know you were up all night
with the baby,

22:52.872 --> 22:54.920
and I really appreciate it.

22:54.944 --> 22:57.453
You know, I'm very grateful

22:57.477 --> 22:59.455
for everything
you've been doing for Lily.

22:59.479 --> 23:02.027
So to thank you, I bought you
a gift certificate to my spa.

23:02.051 --> 23:05.398
And you can take a whole day off
and just really pamper yourself.

23:05.422 --> 23:06.692
Really? Mm-hmm.

23:06.716 --> 23:08.464
Thank you!

23:08.488 --> 23:09.665
Oh, thank you!

23:09.689 --> 23:11.366
Oh, you're welcome.

23:11.390 --> 23:13.669
All right, Lily needs
to be bathed and put to bed.

23:13.693 --> 23:16.642
I don't wanna miss
my yoga class. Hi.

23:16.666 --> 23:20.676
Hi, pretty girl.
Oh, yes, mommy has to go.

23:20.700 --> 23:22.377
Mommy has to go,

23:22.401 --> 23:25.458
so she can stay pretty and thin
and you can be proud of her.

23:27.737 --> 23:29.915
Motherhood is such a blessing.

23:29.939 --> 23:32.409
I hope you get
to experience it one day.

23:37.416 --> 23:39.394
Because
it'snota big deal!

23:39.418 --> 23:40.696
"It's not a big deal"? Okay!

23:40.720 --> 23:43.699
It's not that far away. Right. Oh,
it's not that far away?

23:43.723 --> 23:45.476
Dude, it... whatever, okay?

23:45.500 --> 23:48.133
You didn't even care
to tell me before? Bye.

23:52.431 --> 23:54.480
Justin, what happened?

23:54.504 --> 23:57.491
Andrew just told me he's
moving in with his grandparents.

23:57.515 --> 23:59.485
They live so far away,

23:59.509 --> 24:01.146
I'm never gonna see him anymore.

24:01.170 --> 24:03.670
I'msosorry. I know
that you're good friends.

24:05.975 --> 24:10.095
We're more than friends,
Mrs. Van De Kamp.

24:10.119 --> 24:11.597
I love him.

24:11.621 --> 24:14.121
Oh.

24:16.025 --> 24:17.162
Why?

24:17.186 --> 24:18.904
Why?

24:18.928 --> 24:20.906
Yes. I'd be curious to know

24:20.930 --> 24:24.009
just what it is you see in him.

24:24.033 --> 24:26.950
Well, when my parents
first heard I was gay,

24:26.974 --> 24:28.874
they kicked me out.

24:28.898 --> 24:31.847
They said I had debased
the entire family

24:31.871 --> 24:34.550
and that they couldn't
love me anymore

24:34.574 --> 24:36.181
until I changed.

24:36.205 --> 24:39.825
But Andrew... he said that
ishould be ashamed of them,

24:39.849 --> 24:43.889
'cause they were too stupid
to know how great I was.

24:43.913 --> 24:46.592
That's the thing about Andrew.

24:46.616 --> 24:48.494
He doesn't take crap
from anyone.

24:48.518 --> 24:51.597
How can you not
love someone like that?

24:51.621 --> 24:53.899
You know,
it never ceases to amaze me

24:53.923 --> 24:56.907
how people can turn their backs
on their own family.

24:56.931 --> 24:59.545
I mean... but it happens
every day, doesn't it?

24:59.569 --> 25:00.946
I guess.

25:00.970 --> 25:04.550
You know, Justin, if you
would be willing to help,

25:04.574 --> 25:06.051
I'm pretty sure

25:06.075 --> 25:09.054
that I could find a way
to keep Andrew from moving.

25:09.078 --> 25:11.708
What do you say?

25:16.285 --> 25:17.262
I'm home.

25:17.286 --> 25:18.263
Oh, hi.

25:18.287 --> 25:19.765
Hey, Mrs. McCluskey.

25:19.789 --> 25:22.668
So how did everything go?

25:22.692 --> 25:26.131
Fine. Penny fussed a bit.

25:26.155 --> 25:28.634
I think her molars
are coming in. Oh.

25:28.658 --> 25:30.636
And the twins
fought over the remote.

25:30.660 --> 25:33.138
There's nothing new there.
No.

25:33.162 --> 25:34.640
Here's the big news...

25:34.664 --> 25:38.774
Parker offered me a fudgsicle
if I would show him my vagina.

25:41.240 --> 25:43.719
Oh, good god, Lynette, relax.
I didn't do it.

25:43.743 --> 25:46.697
I just got this
out of the freezer a second ago.

25:46.721 --> 25:48.694
Uh, yeah. Of course. No, sorry.

25:48.718 --> 25:50.996
Apparently, Parker wanted to put
a sunflower seed inside me

25:51.020 --> 25:54.700
and see if a baby would grow.
Where do kids get this stuff?

25:54.724 --> 25:56.531
Oh... that was me.

25:56.555 --> 25:58.834
He was asking about
the birds and the bees,

25:58.858 --> 26:01.558
and I fudged
a few of the details.

26:02.932 --> 26:05.540
Well, he's only 7 years old.

26:05.564 --> 26:08.148
I don't think he needs
to know everything yet.

26:08.172 --> 26:10.816
