of his innocence.

26:10.840 --> 26:12.818
Well, now,
that's where you're wrong.

26:12.842 --> 26:15.550
You get 'em when they're young.

26:15.574 --> 26:17.557
Give them all the gory details.

26:17.581 --> 26:20.185
And then when they're good
and disgusted, you shame 'em.

26:20.209 --> 26:22.728
Excuse me?

26:22.752 --> 26:24.890
You tell them
sex is dirty and wrong

26:24.914 --> 26:26.837
and he shouldn't talk about it,

26:26.861 --> 26:28.834
and if he does,
he's going straight to hell.

26:28.858 --> 26:31.837
That is ridiculous.

26:31.861 --> 26:34.039
Spoken like
a true liberal idiot.

26:34.063 --> 26:35.780
No, I'm not gonna shame my son.

26:35.804 --> 26:38.103
Mm, I'm telling ya, it works.

26:38.127 --> 26:40.676
It keeps people in their place,

26:40.700 --> 26:42.948
it keeps parents
from being humiliated,

26:42.972 --> 26:45.180
and it keeps me from
having to spend the afternoon

26:45.204 --> 26:46.944
talking about my woo-woo.

26:58.918 --> 27:02.798
In your haste to duck out before
the credits rolled, you...

27:02.822 --> 27:06.632
Oh, my god!
Oh, thank you so much.

27:06.656 --> 27:09.635
I stuck a card in there,
just in case you ever wanted

27:09.659 --> 27:11.637
to purposely sit next to me
at a movie, so...

27:11.661 --> 27:15.711
Orson, I'm flattered.
Uh, really.

27:15.735 --> 27:18.043
You...
You don't wanna date me.

27:18.067 --> 27:21.246
I-I mean, my love life is just
so complicated right now.

27:21.270 --> 27:25.320
Well... no, I won't bore you
with the details.

27:25.344 --> 27:28.198
So the ex-boyfriend has no idea
you're secretly married

27:28.222 --> 27:30.195
to the ex-husband,
who still loves you,

27:30.219 --> 27:32.728
but unless you give him
a reason not to,

27:32.752 --> 27:34.660
is gonna marry
the neighborhood slut?

27:34.684 --> 27:36.707
Did I call Edie a slut? Mm-hmm.

27:36.731 --> 27:38.704
Well, that's overstating it.
Edie's not a slut.

27:38.728 --> 27:41.807
