with indiscriminate men.

27:41.831 --> 27:44.710
Anyway... yes, those are
the relevant players.

27:44.734 --> 27:46.647
Okay. Now I'm
absolutely horrified

27:46.671 --> 27:48.944
that I'm about to say
what I'm about to say,

27:48.968 --> 27:51.646
but there's nobody else I can
talk to who won't judge me.

27:51.670 --> 27:53.648
