'cause you know how crazy I am.

28:01.811 --> 28:03.088
So here goes...

28:03.112 --> 28:06.692
I'm having feelings
for Karl again.

28:06.716 --> 28:09.765
Does that make me
a terrible person?

28:09.789 --> 28:12.738
You want my unvarnished opinion?

28:12.762 --> 28:14.840
Lay it on me.

28:14.864 --> 28:16.851
It doesn't make you
a terrible person,

28:16.875 --> 28:18.704
but it does make you a...

28:18.728 --> 28:21.106
Well... a sucker.

28:21.130 --> 28:22.948
This Karl's a coward.

28:22.972 --> 28:26.311
He wants you to be the heavy
and take all the responsibility.

28:26.335 --> 28:27.753
If you're having feelings
for a guy like that,

28:27.777 --> 28:29.985
I say run... Far, far away.

28:30.009 --> 28:31.987
