29:06.816 --> 29:08.854
Bree... I'm so sorry I'm late.

29:08.878 --> 29:10.355
Oh, honey, it's all right.

29:10.379 --> 29:12.357
I mean,
with the new baby at home,

29:12.381 --> 29:14.860
I'm surprised
you made it at all.

29:14.884 --> 29:16.844
Ooh, I'll have a drink.
Anything with an umbrella.

29:18.888 --> 29:22.337
So tell me, how are you doing?

29:22.361 --> 29:24.840
I mean, your entire world
must be turned upside down.

29:24.864 --> 29:27.172
You must be exhausted.

29:27.196 --> 29:30.415
You know, it's been challenging,
but I-I soldier on.

29:30.439 --> 29:32.848
So what about you?
You look so rested.

29:32.872 --> 29:34.880
