a little tense at home,

29:36.911 --> 29:38.884
and I needed an hour to relax.

29:38.908 --> 29:40.886
Good for you. I love that spa.

29:40.910 --> 29:43.358
Mm. Um, oh, by the way,
while I was there,

29:43.382 --> 29:45.390
I saw your, uh,
your housekeeper.

29:45.414 --> 29:47.232
Xiao-Mei?

29:47.256 --> 29:49.234
Oh, no, you must be mistaken.

29:49.258 --> 29:51.797
I just left her.
She's at home working.

29:51.821 --> 29:54.800
