to her in the steam room

29:54.824 --> 29:57.372
for about 20 minutes. What?

29:57.396 --> 29:59.996
Yeah, apparently you gave her
a gift certificate.

30:07.406 --> 30:09.384
Lily?

30:09.408 --> 30:12.108
Lily, mommy's coming!

30:13.883 --> 30:18.123
Oh, thank god!
Oh, honey, I'm so sorry.

30:18.147 --> 30:20.487
I'm never gonna
leave you again. Oh!

30:22.521 --> 30:24.569
Yes. Yes.

30:24.593 --> 30:27.873
I'm home!

30:27.897 --> 30:29.935
