30:29.959 --> 30:32.978
Oh, that's my little girl.

30:33.002 --> 30:35.562
Your chakra lining up nice
for mommy?

30:38.007 --> 30:39.444
That's my girl.

30:39.468 --> 30:42.988
Hey,
let me take her off your chest

30:43.012 --> 30:44.289
so you can do your yoga.

30:44.313 --> 30:46.992
No! No, no, no.
We're doing just fine.

30:47.016 --> 30:48.476
Aren't we, Lily?

31:01.961 --> 31:04.369
Bridezilla's got me
auditioning wedding bands,

31:04.393 --> 31:06.376
and I'm clueless about
Edie's taste in music.

31:06.400 --> 31:08.373
What do you think of these guys?

31:08.397 --> 31:10.375
That's why you brought
me down here? Mm-hmm.

31:10.399 --> 31:12.517
