to help me get my groove on.

31:18.985 --> 31:20.278
Karl... Uh-oh!

31:22.081 --> 31:23.558
Oh, that's right.

31:23.582 --> 31:25.560
You like it laid-back
and romantic, don't you?

31:25.584 --> 31:27.567
Guys, can we play
something mellow?

31:27.591 --> 31:29.564
No, don't bother,
'cause I'm going.

31:29.588 --> 31:31.066
Two...

31:32.121 --> 31:34.639
♪ You are so beautiful... ♪

31:34.663 --> 31:37.933
That was not a coincidence.

31:41.000 --> 31:42.978
This was playing
the night we first kissed.

31:43.002 --> 31:45.911
♪ To me... ♪
it's our song. Remember?

31:45.935 --> 31:48.083
I remember. I also remember that

31:48.107 --> 31:50.155
you are planning
on marrying someone else.

31:50.179 --> 31:52.057
