31:52.081 --> 31:54.659
Come on, susie q.

31:54.683 --> 31:57.170
I can see you still
have feelings for me,

31:57.194 --> 32:00.495
and I know I have
never stopped loving you.

32:00.519 --> 32:01.997
Okay, you want the truth?

32:02.021 --> 32:03.999
I don't know
how I feel about you,

32:04.023 --> 32:06.001
but I keep looking at you,

32:06.025 --> 32:09.004
trying to see if you've changed,
if you've grown up.

32:09.028 --> 32:10.305
You know what I see?

32:10.329 --> 32:12.307
I see the same weak coward

32:12.331 --> 32:15.040
that walked out on me
three years ago.

32:15.064 --> 32:17.012
Of course I've changed.

32:17.036 --> 32:18.413
